      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring a mechanical connection to the rear-wheel-drive platform and its variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The chassis retains its signature handling characteristics through a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a linear power band and the tactile feedback expected of a true M-division icon.",
